name: CoronaryArteryDiseaseSCT
title: Coronary artery disease SCT
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Definition:This value set intends to capture all SNOMED CT codes that represent atherosclerotic heart disease (CAD).),(Data Element Scope: CONDITION: CLINICAL_DRIVER:),(Inclusion Criteria: Codes that are self or descendant of 'coronary arteriosclerosis', 'angina', or 'myocardial infarction'.),(Exclusion Criteria: SNOMED SCT codes that are not representative of atherosclerosis: Coronary artery spasm angina-87343002)
